               <objectContents>
                  <ab type="description">A dozen men waiting in line, approaching a desk with medical and probably other staff. Two women, one of them in white mantel, are working on type-writers. On the large desk in front of them, there is paperwork, a telephone, a cable, some sort of a small aparat, a bottle of coca cola or similar drink. Behind the seated women, there are two men in white mantels, and a third man in light-colored mantel is talking to some of the men that are waiting in line. One of those men and one man in white mantel are looking at the camera. The men enter this room through a door, and behind the door there are few other men who take a look in the room and wait their turn.</ab>
                  <ab type="comment">It is unclear whether the medical team is brought into the factory, or whether the workers are brought to the medical center for examinaton.</ab>
               </objectContents>
